Package: astro-ai-assistant
Version: 1.0.0-alpha.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.28), libstdc++6 (>= 8), zlib1g (>= 1:1.2.0), libssl3 | libssl1.1, libicu72 | libicu70 | libicu67 | libicu66 | libicu65 | libicu63, libffi8 | libffi7
Recommends: python3 (>= 3.11)
Maintainer: Douglas Mitchell <senpai-sama7@proton.me>
Homepage: https://github.com/Senpai-Sama7/Astro
Description: AI-powered assistant for task automation
 ASTRO (Autonomous System for Task and Resource Orchestration)
 is an AI-powered assistant that helps automate tasks through
 natural conversation. It features:
 .
 - Natural language command processing
 - Multi-layer security architecture
 - File and system management
 - Web search capabilities
 - Code analysis and execution
 - Both sync (astro_shell) and async (vibe_shell) CLI interfaces
 .
 This package includes the complete ASTRO system with all
 dependencies bundled for standalone operation.
